posts.post_title: C46 Lot of 62 poor condition cards for sale
posts.post_content:

The lot includes Gandil, McGinnity, Demmitt, and Dunn. I have attached pics of the very worst in the lot as well as some of the better condition ones. I can send more detailed pics if requested.
